    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the leather remains supple and taut, and every electronic component and feature functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in its original, factory-new state.",
