      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine. This unit boasts a crisp throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system that has been professionally addressed. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is well-sorted, with the critical subframe reinforcement already completed and a suspension refresh utilizing polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in. While the exterior shows the light patina of a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust and the valve clearances were recently shimmed to spec. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning pilot.",
